    "They also support waste management by repurposing industrial and agricultural by-products.",
    "However, there are challenges, such as potential reductions in workability and early-age strength and inconsistencies in quality and supply.",
    "Selecting SCMs requires careful consideration of the specific needs of the project and the properties of the materials available. 7.",
    "SCMs offer significant environmental and economic advantages in cement production.",
    "Low-cost SCMs like FA and POFA are highly sustainable, with minimal emissions and affordability, making them ideal for environmentally conscious projects."
